The Federation of Kuwaiti Engineering Of: The Kuwaiti Federation of Engineering Offices and Consultant Houses was established on Sunday 23/4/2006 AD by virtue of Law No. 38 of 1964, an organized body under the name (Kuwaiti Federation of Engineering Offices and Consultant Houses) located in Kuwait City

The Kuwaiti Federation of Engineering Offices and Consultant Houses seeks to take care of the interests of members, defend their rights, represent engineering offices and advisory houses in front of official bodies, companies and Arab and foreign bodies, and propose rules and regulations that lead to raising the level of the engineering profession, engineering competitions, contributions and review of standard specifications in cooperation with the competent bodies
